Package org.github.fussel178.telestion.extension.corfu.corfu.mapper

package org.github.fussel178.telestion.extension.corfu.corfu.mapper
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    CorfuAppMapper
    This class implements a Corfu app transformer that can map CorfuAppTelemetry and CorfuAppTelecommand from their binary format into a JsonMessage format and back.
    CorfuMessageMapper
    This class implements a message transformer that can map CorfuTelemetry and CorfuTelecommand from their binary format into a JsonMessage format and back.
    CorfuNodeMapper
    This class implements a Corfu node transformer that can map CorfuNode and CorfuHardware from their binary format into a JsonMessage format and back.
    CorfuPayloadMapper
    This class implements a Corfu payload transformer that can map AppTelemetryPayload and AppTelecommandPayload from their binary format into a JsonMessage format and back.
    DefaultValues
    Defaults values that should be used when payload fields inside CorfuPayloads does not have the CorfuProperty annotation and need to be filled in to allow instantiation of the record.
    PayloadField
    Represents a field in a CorfuPayload.
    PayloadFieldArrays
    Utility class to handle arrays of PayloadFields in a better way.
